@baseUrl = http://localhost:5236/api/v1

### Get All Communities
GET {{baseUrl}}/Communities
Accept: application/json

### Get Community by Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/Communities/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

### Create Community without Image
POST {{baseUrl}}/communities
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

New Community
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

This is a test community description
------FormBoundary--

### Create Community with Image (using multipart/form-data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/communities
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Community with Image
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Community with uploaded image
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------FormBoundary--

### Update Community without Image
PUT {{baseUrl}}/communities/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Updated Community Name
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Updated Community Description
------FormBoundary--

### Update Community with new Image
PUT {{baseUrl}}/communities/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Updated Community Name
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Updated Community Description
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="new-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------FormBoundary--

### Delete Community
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/communities/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
